    "description": "Aya: Tale of Tails is a beautiful third-person exploration game where a life story ends and another one is about to begin.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366950/extras/70f4bbca50b8d9417426c357b0412e7d.poster.avif?t=1715210761\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366950/extras/70f4bbca50b8d9417426c357b0412e7d.webm?t=1715210761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366950/extras/70f4bbca50b8d9417426c357b0412e7d.mp4?t=1715210761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Once upon a time...</strong><br><br>On a cold, yet enchanted winter night, after a recent family loss, a young girl gets read a storybook by her father and enters its ancient, magical world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366950/extras/ebe41531803b52535b471633e6798037.poster.avif?t=1715210761\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366950/extras/ebe41531803b52535b471633e6798037.webm?t=1715210761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366950/extras/ebe41531803b52535b471633e6798037.mp4?t=1715210761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>You write your own story</strong><br><br>Meet and play the role of Aya's new friend - a mystical white wolf and together explore the mysterious faraway lands and their hidden tales. Begin a <i>high-spirited</i> journey, make new friends, save lives and discover your true selves in the mysterious land of tales.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366950/extras/f59ad524d88273cfe1732cee8094206f.poster.avif?t=1715210761\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366950/extras/f59ad524d88273cfe1732cee8094206f.webm?t=1715210761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366950/extras/f59ad524d88273cfe1732cee8094206f.mp4?t=1715210761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> For fans of adventure story driven games like Journey, Firewatch and Stray.<br></li><li> A relatively short game focused on story with some light objectives, puzzle solving and platforming.<br></li><li> An emotional soundtrack, with an even more emotional story made by a solo indie developer.<br></li><li> Each update will unfold a new chapter with new lands and stories to discover.<br></li><li> Supports a fan-translation system for subtitles (see Steam forums for details).</li></ul>",
